text: Gymnocarpos bracteatus is a species of plant in the family Caryophyllaceae. It is endemic to Yemen. Its natural habitat is subtropical or tropical dry shrubland. ==References== Category:Endemic flora of Socotra Category:Caryophyllaceae Category:Vulnerable plants Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot Category:Taxa named by Isaac Bayley Balfour
